{"tid":942180,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個精神病康復者 長文慎入","createTime":"2018-12-15T12:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T10:37:15.000Z","uid":31182,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4637be84a2f265e9e7da8909883378c41143ebb7","tid":942180,"uid":31182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:45:14.000Z","msg":"我係一個精神病康復者<br />\n我患上咗躁鬱症<br />\n住咗兩個幾月院後終於可以出院<br />\n點知一出院就失戀<br />\n個女朋友仲要係一齊咗6年<br />\n好多朋友都以為我哋會修成正果，奈何結果唔係咁<br />\n當我得到自由，隨即就失去愛人<br />\n個天好似想玩我咁<br />\n其實我係抵死<br />\n一齊咗咁多年，咩幸福都畀唔到佢，仲妄想同人結婚，真係笑死人<br />\n有一晚佢放工，畀人搶嘢，但作為男朋友嘅我竟然冇出去陪佢，簡直係枉為人<br />\n仲有太多太多事對佢唔住，不能盡錄<br />\n而家為咗佢，又有自殺念頭，應該要再次入院<br />\n我講咁多都係純發洩，多謝大家"},{"pid":"8539b9d48483074e88d6979e3cea5abaa8f16333","tid":942180,"uid":185410,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:49:44.000Z","msg":"咁叫長文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c68399faf768f46ce5e6c3607b328f1c51dbfaa0","tid":942180,"uid":157305,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:51:08.000Z","msg":"此帖必火 🔥 🔥 🔥"},{"pid":"6511f5c1afa90ab0ac79ff1bf6a0478b5dd18f8a","tid":942180,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🤷&zwj;♂️🤷&zwj;♂️🤷&zwj;♂️</span>"},{"pid":"d1c13d0ab2a03d8f4b6d059f83f5795d725ccd1c","tid":942180,"uid":224847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:45:23.000Z","msg":"有冇多啲？"},{"pid":"5069f407344e3f9fce42372953a60672b9dfbc11","tid":942180,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"成日ff人哋迫害你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d967bd3b91416277ab3e7f893381f4420eba7c","tid":942180,"uid":31182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1c13d0ab